&lt;p>In this talk I will discuss with about &amp;ldquo;Argument&amp;rdquo;&lt;br>
People think Argument is bad. &lt;br>
You can think, and ask yourself, &lt;br>
Is Argument really bad? &lt;br>
We will discussed that here.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>An argument is a structured series of&lt;br>
sentences, statements, or propositions,&lt;br>
where some serve as premises leading to a conclusion.&lt;br>
This logical framework is not just confined&lt;br>
to philosophy or debate but is also fundamental to both&lt;br>
scientific inquiry and spiritual exploration.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>